--- !u!114 &543205893
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 543205891}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 667ee28ba5310a34c9adc74449d1d684, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InteractableObject
  dialogueLines:
  - text: Musang!!
    speaker: Para Hewan
    portrait: {fileID: -8659368497797364039, guid: 54b4f4a3359007a499595a52b7b0063a, type: 3}
  - text: Aku kembali teman-teman
    speaker: Musang
    portrait: {fileID: -3690644101301664431, guid: 429de3cd8b8784544a4a252807409d4f, type: 3}
  - text: Apakah kau terluka?
    speaker: Monyet
    portrait: {fileID: 6509476210618258023, guid: 54b4f4a3359007a499595a52b7b0063a, type: 3}
  - text: 'Tidak, aku diselamatkan oleh Orang Utan '
    speaker: Musang
    portrait: {fileID: -7336199843773729760, guid: 429de3cd8b8784544a4a252807409d4f, type: 3}
  - text: Syukurlah kamu baik baik saja
    speaker: Tupai
    portrait: {fileID: 6411604176296474208, guid: c9270b0fbe0fba244b204836e134bac1, type: 3}
  - text: (Hmm, hutan ini terlalu luas)
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: -6668896378578197248, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: (Aku harus menanyakan pada mereka, cara keluar dari Hutan ini)
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 7933640903824198564, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: Apakah kalian tau cara keluar dari Hutan ini?
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: Sudah lama kami hidup di Hutan luas ini
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: 687e4c0dc0dfdb84a881fc7d9f6da4bd, type: 3}
  - text: Tidak terpikir kami mencari jalan keluar dari Hutan
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: 687e4c0dc0dfdb84a881fc7d9f6da4bd, type: 3}
  - text: Coba kamu tanyakan pada Kudanil
    speaker: Musang
    portrait: {fileID: -7336199843773729760, guid: 429de3cd8b8784544a4a252807409d4f, type: 3}
  - text: Mungkin dia tau jawaban yang kamu cari
    speaker: Tupai
    portrait: {fileID: -20588519564721322, guid: c9270b0fbe0fba244b204836e134bac1, type: 3}
  - text: Di mana Kudanil itu?
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: 'Dia ada di Hutan Barat '
    speaker: Musang
    portrait: {fileID: -7336199843773729760, guid: 429de3cd8b8784544a4a252807409d4f, type: 3}
  - text: Aku dengar dia terjebak diantara para predator air
    speaker: Musang
    portrait: {fileID: -3230606766609994181, guid: 429de3cd8b8784544a4a252807409d4f, type: 3}
  - text: '!!!'
    speaker: Para hewan
    portrait: {fileID: -8579099847079376591, guid: c9270b0fbe0fba244b204836e134bac1, type: 3}
  - text: (Aku harus menyelamatkan dia, mungkin dia tau informasi tentang Hutan ini)
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: Aku akan pergi selamatkan dia
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
  - text: Kami tidak berani ikut pergi
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: 687e4c0dc0dfdb84a881fc7d9f6da4bd, type: 3}
  - text: Para pengganggu itu pasti akan menghajar kami
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 1199990940518312585, guid: 687e4c0dc0dfdb84a881fc7d9f6da4bd, type: 3}
  - text: Tenang saja
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: dc05296099fd74a4d94472e7d3817c5e, type: 3}
