--- !u!114 &1592051487
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1592051486}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8f4a2ab63b400b44f8c3f9a3691e0eb9, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EventAreaTrigger
  triggerOnce: 1
  useInitialDelay: 1
  initialDelayDuration: 0.5
  useFadeIn: 0
  useFadeOut: 0
  cameraTarget: {fileID: 2103809974}
  cameraStayDuration: 1
  useSmoothPan: 1
  panSpeed: 3
  playerWalkTarget: {fileID: 1292403518}
  playerWalkStopDistance: 0.15
  movePlayerAtDialogIndex: 2
  useDialogue: 1
  dialogueLines:
  - text: Ada hewan-hewan lain di sini...
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: Aku akan coba tanyakan kepada mereka
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: Orang Utan!!
    speaker: Tupai
    portrait: {fileID: 2755192431615705251, guid: e74192485374e2c478d756bf87367270, type: 3}
  - text: Darimana saja kamu?!
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 1199990940518312585, guid: f609edebf34f0514d8a4bcb783e532ad, type: 3}
  - text: (Hewan bisa berbicara?)
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: Syukurlah kamu baik baik saja
    speaker: Monyet
    portrait: {fileID: 666493126454615707, guid: e27a4bff15be3674482f378a759a4c4c, type: 3}
  - text: Orang Utan, apakah kamu melihat hewan yang lain?
    speaker: Tupai
    portrait: {fileID: 5023720081623843394, guid: e74192485374e2c478d756bf87367270, type: 3}
  - text: Maksud kamu siapa?
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: ...
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: f609edebf34f0514d8a4bcb783e532ad, type: 3}
  - text: Sepertinya kamu kelelahan ya
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: f609edebf34f0514d8a4bcb783e532ad, type: 3}
  - text: Kita semua ini terpisah karena ada pengganggu di hutan ini
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 1199990940518312585, guid: f609edebf34f0514d8a4bcb783e532ad, type: 3}
  - text: Kami sekarang sedang beristirahat, karena kelelahan
    speaker: Rusa
    portrait: {fileID: 3025518587304049201, guid: f609edebf34f0514d8a4bcb783e532ad, type: 3}
  - text: ...
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: Kalau begitu aku ikut mencari yang lainnya
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: Jangan, nanti kamu tersesat lagi
    speaker: Monyet
    portrait: {fileID: 6509476210618258023, guid: e27a4bff15be3674482f378a759a4c4c, type: 3}
  - text: Tidak apa-apa, selagi aku masih bisa bergerak. Aku bisa membantu kalian
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  - text: (Mungkin aku bisa mencari jalan keluar dari Hutan ini)
    speaker: Bara
    portrait: {fileID: 5319344114519903559, guid: d41cf00244fce9c4aabf92e25b57b398, type: 3}
  moveCameraAtDialogIndex: 0
  returnCameraAtDialogIndex: 2
  useQuest: 1
  requiredQuest: 5
  nextQuest: 7
  triggerOncePersistent: 1
  customPersistentKey: 
